#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:3684
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISPMT"
msgstr "ISPMT"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3685
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calculates the interest paid on a given period of an investment."
msgstr "Beräknar räntan som betalas för en given period och investering."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3687
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Period is the amortizement period. 1 for the first and NPer for the last "
"period."
msgstr ""
"Period är amorteringsperioden. 1 för den första och APER för den sista "
"perioden."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3688
#, no-c-format
msgid "NPer is the total number of periods during which annuity is paid."
msgstr "APER är totalt antal perioder som det periodiska beloppet betalas."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3694
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISPMT(Rate; Period; NPer; PV)"
msgstr "ISPMT(Räntesats; Period; APER; AV)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:3701
#, no-c-format
msgid "Present values (PV)"
msgstr "Aktuella värden (AV)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3704
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISPMT(0.1; 1; 3; 8000000) equals -533333"
msgstr "ISPMT(0,1; 1; 3; 8000000) är lika med -533333"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:3719
#, no-c-format
msgid "LEVEL_COUPON"
msgstr "LEVEL_COUPON"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The LEVEL_COUPON() function calculates the value of a level-coupon bond. For "
"example: if the interest rate is 10%, a $1000 bond with semi-annual coupons "
"at a rate of 13% that matures in 4 years is worth "
"LEVEL_COUPON(1000;.13;2;4;.1) or $1096.95."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen LEVEL_COUPON() beräknar värdet av en kupongförsedd obligation. "
"Till exempel: om räntesatsen är 10%, så blir en 1 000 kr obligation med "
"halvårskuponger med en kupongsats på 13% som förfaller på 4 år värd "
"LEVEL_COUPON(1000;13;2;4;0,1) eller 1 096,95 kr."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3725
#, no-c-format
msgid "LEVEL_COUPON(face value;coupon rate;coupons per year;years;market rate)"
msgstr ""
"LEVEL_COUPON(nominellt värde;kupongsats;kuponger per år;år;marknadskurs)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:3729 functions.docbook:4436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Face value"
msgstr "Valör"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:3730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coupon rate"
msgstr "Kupongsats"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:3731
#, no-c-format
msgid "Coupons per year"
msgstr "Kuponger per år"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:3733
#, no-c-format
msgid "Market interest rate"
msgstr "Marknadsränta"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3736
#, no-c-format
msgid "LEVEL_COUPON(1000;.13;2;4;.1) equals 1096.95"
msgstr "LEVEL_COUPON(1000;0,13;2;4;0,1) är lika med 1 096,95"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:3742
#, no-c-format
msgid "MDURATION"
msgstr "MDURATION"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The MDURATION() function will calculate the modified Macauley duration of a "
"fixed interest security in years."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen MDURATION() beräknar modifierad räntebindningstid för ett "
"värdepapper med fast räntesats i år."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3748
#, no-c-format
msgid "MDURATION( Settlement; Maturity; Coupon; Yield; Frequency; [ Basis=0 ])"
msgstr ""
"MDURATION(Avräkning; Förfaller; Kupong; Avkastning; Frekvens; [ Bas=0 ])"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"MDURATION(\"2004-02-01\"; \"2004-05-31\"; 0.08; 0.09; 2; 0) returns "
"0.316321106"
msgstr ""
"MDURATION(\"2004-02-01\"; \"2004-05-31\"; 0,08; 0,09; 2; 0) returnerar "
"0,316321106"

#. Tag: member
#: functions.docbook:3764
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"DURATION\">DURATION</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"DURATION\">DURATION</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:3771
#, no-c-format
msgid "MIRR"
msgstr "MIRR"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3772
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The MIRR() function will calculate the modified internal rate of return "
"(IRR) of a series of periodic investments."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen MIRR() beräknar den modifierade internräntan för en serie "
"periodiska investeringar."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:3777
#, no-c-format
