msgid "ISNOTTEXT"
msgstr "ISNOTTEXT"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISNOTTEXT() function returns True if the parameter is not a string. "
"Otherwise it returns False. It's the same as ISNONTEXT."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISNOTTEXT() returnerar True om parametern inte är en textsträng, "
"annars returneras False. Den är samma som ISNONTEXT."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4726
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNOTTEXT(x)"
msgstr "ISNOTTEXT(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4733
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNOTTEXT(12) returns True"
msgstr "ISNOTTEXT(12) returnerar True"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4736
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNOTTEXT(\"hello\") returns False"
msgstr "ISNOTTEXT(\"hello\") returnerar False"

#. Tag: member
#: functions.docbook:4740
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"ISNONTEXT\">ISNONTEXT</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"ISNONTEXT\">ISNONTEXT</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4747
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUM"
msgstr "ISNUM"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4748
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISNUM() function returns True if the parameter is a numerical value. "
"Otherwise it returns False. It's the same as ISNUMBER."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISNUM() returnerar sant om parametern är ett numeriskt värde, "
"annars returneras falskt. Den är samma som ISNUMBER."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4753
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUM(x)"
msgstr "ISNUM(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4760
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUM(12) returns True"
msgstr "ISNUM(12) returnerar True"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4763
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUM(hello) returns False"
msgstr "ISNUM(hello) returnerar False"

#. Tag: member
#: functions.docbook:4767
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"ISNUMBER\">ISNUMBER</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"ISNUMBER\">ISNUMBER</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4774
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUMBER"
msgstr "ISNUMBER"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISNUMBER() function returns True if the parameter is a numerical value. "
"Otherwise it returns False. It's the same as ISNUM."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISNUMBER() returnerar sant om parametern är ett numeriskt värde, "
"annars returneras falskt. Den är samma som ISNUM."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4780
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUMBER(x)"
msgstr "ISNUMBER(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4787
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUMBER(12) returns True"
msgstr "ISNUMBER(12) returnerar True"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4790
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISNUMBER(hello) returns False"
msgstr "ISNUMBER(hello) returnerar False"

#. Tag: member
#: functions.docbook:4794
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"ISNUM\">ISNUM</link>&nbsp;"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"ISNUM\">ISNUM</link>&nbsp;"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4801
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISODD"
msgstr "ISODD"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4802
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISODD() function returns True if the number is odd. Otherwise returns "
"False."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISODD() returnerar sant om talet är udda, annars returneras "
"falskt."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4807
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISODD(x)"
msgstr "ISODD(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4814
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISODD(12) returns False"
msgstr "ISODD(12) returnerar False"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4817
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISODD(-7) returns True"
msgstr "ISODD(-7) returnerar True"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4823
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISREF"
msgstr "ISREF"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISREF() function returns True if the parameter refers to a reference. "
"Otherwise it returns False"
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISREF() returnerar True om parametern anger en referens, annars "
"returneras False"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4829
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISREF(x)"
msgstr "ISREF(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4836
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISREF(A12) returns true"
msgstr "ISREF(A12) returnerar true"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4839
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISREF(\"hello\") returns false"
msgstr "ISREF(\"hallå\") returnerar false"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4845
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTEXT"
msgstr "ISTEXT"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4846
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISTEXT() function returns True if the parameter is a string. Otherwise "
"it returns False"
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISTEXT() returnerar True om parametern är en textsträng, annars "
"returneras False"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4851
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTEXT(x)"
msgstr "ISTEXT(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4858
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTEXT(12) returns False"
msgstr "ISTEXT(12) returnerar False"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4861
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTEXT(\"hello\") returns True"
msgstr "ISTEXT(\"hello\") returnerar True"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4867
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTIME"
msgstr "ISTIME"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4868
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ISTIME() function returns True if the parameter is a time value. "
"Otherwise it returns False."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen ISTIME() returnerar sant om parametern är ett tidsvärde, annars "
"returneras falskt."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4873
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTIME(x)"
msgstr "ISTIME(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4880
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTIME(\"12:05\") returns True"
msgstr "ISTIME(\"12:05\") returnerar True"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4883
#, no-c-format
msgid "ISTIME(\"hello\") returns False"
msgstr "ISTIME(\"hallå\") returnerar False"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4889
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>N</title>"
msgstr "<title>N</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4890
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The N() function converts a value to a number. If value is or refers to a "
"number, this function returns the number. If value is True, this function "
"returns 1. If a value is a date, this function returns the serial number of "
"that date. Anything else will cause the function to return 0."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen N() konverterar ett värdet till ett tal. Om värdet är, eller "
"refererar till ett tal, så returnerar funktionen talet. Om värdet är True, "
"så returnerar funktionen 1. Om värdet är ett datum, returnerar funktionen "
"det datumets serienummer. Allt annat gör att funktionen returnerar 0."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4895
#, no-c-format
msgid "N(value)"
msgstr "N(värde)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4902
#, no-c-format
msgid "N(3.14) returns 3.14"
msgstr "N(3,14) returnerar 3,14"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4905
#, no-c-format
msgid "N(\"7\") returns 0 (because \"7\" is text)"
msgstr "N(\"7\") returnerar 0 (eftersom \"7\" är text)"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4911
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>NA</title>"
msgstr "<title>NA</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4912
#, no-c-format
msgid "The NA() function returns the constant error value, N/A."
msgstr "Funktionen NA() returnerar det konstanta felvärdet, INTE TILLGÄNGLIG."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4917
#, no-c-format
msgid "NA()"
msgstr "NA()"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4933
#, no-c-format
msgid "TYPE"
msgstr "TYPE"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4934
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The TYPE() function returns 1 if the value is a number, 2 if it is text, 4 "
"if the value is a logical value, 16 if it is an error value or 64 if the "
"value is an array. If the cell the value represents contains a formula you "
"get its return type."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen TYPE() returnerar 1 om värdet är ett tal, 2 om det är text, 4 om "
"det är ett logiskt värde, 16 om det är ett felvärde eller 64 om värdet är en "
"lista. Om cellen värdet representerar innehåller en formel, returneras dess "
"returtyp."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4940
#, no-c-format
msgid "TYPE(x)"
msgstr "TYPE(x)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4947
#, no-c-format
msgid "TYPE(A1) returns 2, if A1 contains \"Text\""
msgstr "TYPE(A1) returnerar 2, om A1 innehåller \"Text\""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4950
#, no-c-format
msgid "TYPE(-7) returns 1"
msgstr "TYPE(-7) returnerar 1"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4953
#, no-c-format
msgid "TYPE(A2) returns 1, if A2 contains \"=CURRENTDATE()\""
msgstr "TYPE(A2) returnerar 1, om A2 innehåller \"=CURRENTDATE()\""

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logical"
msgstr "Logisk"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4962
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>AND</title>"
msgstr "<title>AND</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4963
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The AND() function returns True if all the values are true. Otherwise it "
"returns False (unless any of the values in an error - then it returns an "
"error)."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen AND() returnerar sant om alla värden är sanna, annars returneras "
"falskt (om inte något av värdena är fel, då returnerar den ett fel)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4968
#, no-c-format
msgid "AND(value;value;...)"
msgstr "AND(värde;värde;...)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:4972 functions.docbook:4973 functions.docbook:4974
#: functions.docbook:4975 functions.docbook:4976 functions.docbook:5077
#: functions.docbook:5078 functions.docbook:5079 functions.docbook:5080
#: functions.docbook:5081 functions.docbook:5103 functions.docbook:5104
#: functions.docbook:5105 functions.docbook:5106 functions.docbook:5107
#: functions.docbook:5151 functions.docbook:5152 functions.docbook:5153
#: functions.docbook:5154 functions.docbook:5155 functions.docbook:5195
#: functions.docbook:5196 functions.docbook:5197 functions.docbook:5198
#: functions.docbook:5199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Boolean values"
msgstr "Booleska värden"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:4972 functions.docbook:4973 functions.docbook:4974
#: functions.docbook:4975 functions.docbook:4976 functions.docbook:5077
#: functions.docbook:5078 functions.docbook:5079 functions.docbook:5080
#: functions.docbook:5081 functions.docbook:5103 functions.docbook:5104
#: functions.docbook:5105 functions.docbook:5106 functions.docbook:5107
#: functions.docbook:5151 functions.docbook:5152 functions.docbook:5153
#: functions.docbook:5154 functions.docbook:5155 functions.docbook:5195
#: functions.docbook:5196 functions.docbook:5197 functions.docbook:5198
#: functions.docbook:5199
#, no-c-format
msgid "A range of truth values (TRUE or FALSE)"
msgstr "Ett område med booleska värden (TRUE eller FALSE)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4979
#, no-c-format
msgid "AND(true;true;true) returns True"
msgstr "AND(Sant;Sant;Sant) returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4982
#, no-c-format
msgid "AND(true;false) returns False"
msgstr "AND(Sant;Falsk) returnerar Falsk"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:4988
#, no-c-format
msgid "FALSE"
msgstr "FALSE"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4989
#, no-c-format
msgid "The FALSE() function returns the boolean value FALSE."
msgstr "Funktionen FALSE() returnerar det booleska värdet FALSK."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:4994
#, no-c-format
msgid "FALSE()"
msgstr "FALSE()"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5000
#, no-c-format
msgid "FALSE() returns FALSE"
msgstr "FALSE() returnerar FALSK"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5006
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>IF</title>"
msgstr "<title>IF</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The IF() function is a conditional function. This function returns the "
"second parameter if the condition is True. Otherwise it returns the third "
"parameter (which defaults to being false)."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen IF() är en villkorlig funktion. Denna funktion returnerar den "
"andra parametern om villkoret är sant, annars returneras den tredje "
"parametern (som har standardvärdet falskt)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5012
#, no-c-format
msgid "IF(condition;if_true;if_false)"
msgstr "IF(villkor;om_sant;om_falskt)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Condition"
msgstr "Villkor"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5017
#, no-c-format
msgid "If true"
msgstr "om sant"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5018
#, no-c-format
msgid "If false"
msgstr "om falskt"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5021
#, no-c-format
msgid "A1=4;A2=6;IF(A1>A2;5;3) returns 3"
msgstr "A1=4;A2=6;IF(A1>A2;5;3) returnerar 3"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5027
#, no-c-format
msgid "IFERROR"
msgstr "IFERROR"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5028
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Return X unless it is an Error, in which case return an alternative value."
msgstr ""
"Returnera X om inte ett fel inträffar, returnera då ett alternativt värde."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5033
#, no-c-format
msgid "IFERROR(AnyX;AnyAlternative)"
msgstr "IFERROR(X;Alternativ)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5037 functions.docbook:5057
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any X"
msgstr "X"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5038 functions.docbook:5058
#, no-c-format
msgid "Any Alternative"
msgstr "Alternativ"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5041
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"IFERROR(A1;A2) returns the content of A1 if that content is not an error-"
"value else the content of A2 is returned."
msgstr ""
"IFERROR(A1;A2) returnera innehållet i A1 om innehållet inte är ett felvärde, "
"annars returnera A2."

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5047
#, no-c-format
msgid "IFNA"
msgstr "IFNA"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5048
#, no-c-format
msgid "Return X unless it is an NA, in which case return an alternative value."
msgstr "Returnera X om det inte är NA, returnera då ett alternativt värde."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5053
#, no-c-format
msgid "IFNA(AnyX;AnyAlternative)"
msgstr "IFNA(X;Alternativ)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5061
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"IFNA(A1;A2) returns the content of A1 if that content is not an #N/A error-"
"value else the content of A2 is returned."
msgstr ""
"IFNA(A1;A2) returnera innehållet i A1 om innehållet inte är ett #INTE "
"TILLGÄNGLIG felvärde, annars returnera A2."

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5067
#, no-c-format
msgid "NAND"
msgstr "NAND"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The NAND() function returns True if at least one value is not true. "
"Otherwise it returns False."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen NAND() returnerar sant om minst ett av värdena inte är sant, "
"annars returneras falskt."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5073
#, no-c-format
msgid "NAND(value;value;...)"
msgstr "NAND(värde;värde;...)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5084
#, no-c-format
msgid "NAND(true;false;false) returns True"
msgstr "NAND(Sant;Falsk;Falsk) returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5087
#, no-c-format
msgid "NAND(true;true) returns False"
msgstr "NAND(Sann;Sann) returnerar Falsk"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5093
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>NOR</title>"
msgstr "<title>NOR</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The NOR() function returns True if all the values given as parameters are of "
"boolean type and have the value false. Otherwise it returns False."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen NOR() returnerar sant om alla värden är av typen boolesk och har "
"värdet falskt, annars returnerar den falskt."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5099
#, no-c-format
msgid "NOR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "NOR(värde;värde;...)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5110
#, no-c-format
msgid "NOR(true;false;false) returns False"
msgstr "NOR(Sann;Falsk;Falsk) returnerar Falsk"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5113
#, no-c-format
msgid "NOR(false;false) returns True"
msgstr "NOR(false;false) returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5119
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>NOT</title>"
msgstr "<title>NOT</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The NOT() function returns True if the value is False and returns False if "
"the value is True. It returns an error if the input in an error."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen NOT() returnerar sant om värdet är falskt och returnerar falskt "
"om värdet är sant. Den returnerar ett fel om indata är fel."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5125
#, no-c-format
msgid "NOT(bool)"
msgstr "NOT(boolesk)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Boolean value"
msgstr "Booleskt värde"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5132
#, no-c-format
msgid "NOT(false) returns True"
msgstr "NOT(Falsk) returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5135
#, no-c-format
msgid "NOT(true) returns False"
msgstr "NOT(Sant) returnerar Falsk"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>OR</title>"
msgstr "<title>OR</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The OR() function returns True if at least one of the values is true. "
"Otherwise it returns False (unless any of the values is an error, then it "
"returns an error)."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen OR() returnerar sant om minst ett av värdena är sant, annars "
"returneras falskt (om inte något av värdena är fel, då returnerar den ett "
"fel)."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5147
#, no-c-format
msgid "OR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "OR(värde;värde;...)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5158
#, no-c-format
msgid "OR(false;false;false) returns False"
msgstr "OR(Falsk;Falsk;Falsk) returnerar Falsk"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5161
#, no-c-format
msgid "OR(true;false) returns True"
msgstr "OR(Sant;Falsk) returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5167
#, no-c-format
msgid "TRUE"
msgstr "TRUE"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5168
#, no-c-format
msgid "The TRUE() function returns the boolean value TRUE."
msgstr "Funktionen TRUE() returnerar det booleska värdet Sann."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5173
#, no-c-format
msgid "TRUE()"
msgstr "TRUE()"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5179
#, no-c-format
msgid "TRUE() returns TRUE"
msgstr "TRUE() returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>XOR</title>"
msgstr "<title>XOR</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The XOR() function returns False if the number of True values is even. "
"Otherwise it returns True. It returns an error if any argument is an error."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen XOR() returnerar falskt om antalet sanna värden är jämnt, annars "
"returneras sant. Den returnerar ett fel om något argument är fel."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5191
#, no-c-format
msgid "XOR(value;value;...)"
msgstr "XOR(värde;värde;...)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5202
#, no-c-format
msgid "XOR(false;false;false) returns True"
msgstr "XOR(Falsk;Falsk;Falsk) returnerar Falsk"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5205
#, no-c-format
msgid "XOR(true;false) returns True"
msgstr "XOR(Sant;Falskt) returnerar Sann"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lookup &amp; Reference"
msgstr "Uppslagning och referens"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5214
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS"
msgstr "ADDRESS"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The ADDRESS creates a cell address. Parameter Row is the row number and "
"Column is the column number."
msgstr ""
"ADDRESS skapar en celladress. Parametern rad är radnumret och kol är "
"kolumnnumret."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Absolute number specifies the type of reference: 1 or omitted = Absolute, 2 "
"= Absolute row, relative column, 3 = Relative row; absolute column and 4 = "
"Relative."
msgstr ""
"Talet absolut anger referenstypen: 1 eller utelämnad = absolut, 2 = absolut "
"rad, relativ kolumn, 3 = relativ rad, absolut kolumn och 4 = relativ."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A1 Style specifies the style of the address to return. If A1 is set to TRUE "
"(default) the address is returned in A1 style if it is set to FALSE in R1C1 "
"style."
msgstr ""
"A1-stil anger stilen för adressen som returneras. Om A1 är TRUE (förval) "
"returneras adressen med A1-stil. Om den är FALSE returneras adressen med "
"R1C1-stil."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet name is the text specifying the name of the sheet."
msgstr "Arbetsbladsnamn är texten som anger namnet på bladet."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5223
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS(row; col; absolute; style; sheet name)"
msgstr "ADDRESS(rad; kol; absolut; stil; arbetsbladsnamn)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Row number"
msgstr "Radnummer"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Column number"
msgstr "Kolumn-nummer"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5229
#, no-c-format
msgid "Absolute number (optional)"
msgstr "Absolutvärde (valfritt)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5230 functions.docbook:5434
#, no-c-format
msgid "A1 style (optional)"
msgstr "A1-stil (valfri)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet name"
msgstr "Arbetsbladsnamn"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5234
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4) returns $D$6"
msgstr "ADDRESS(6; 4) returnerar $D$6"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5237
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 2) returns D$6"
msgstr "ADDRESS(6; 4; 2) returnerar D$6"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5240
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 2; FALSE; \"Sheet1\") returns Sheet1!R6C[4]"
msgstr "ADDRESS(6; 4; 2; FALSE; \"Blad1\") returnerar Blad1!R6C[4]"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5243
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 1; FALSE; \"Sheet1\") returns Sheet1!R6C4"
msgstr "ADDRESS(6; 4; 1; FALSE; \"Blad1\") returnerar Blad1!R6C4"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5246
#, no-c-format
msgid "ADDRESS(6; 4; 4; TRUE; \"Sheet1\") returns Sheet1!D6"
msgstr "ADDRESS(6; 4; 4; TRUE; \"Blad1\") returnerar Blad1!D6"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5252
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREAS"
msgstr "AREAS"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns the number of areas in the reference string. An area can be asingle "
"cell or a set of cells."
msgstr ""
"Returnerar antalet områden i referenssträngen. Ett område kan vara en "
"enstaka cell eller ett antal celler."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5258
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREAS(reference)"
msgstr "AREAS(referens)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5265
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREAS(A1) returns 1"
msgstr "AREAS(A1) returnerar 1"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5268
#, no-c-format
msgid "AREAS((A1; A2:A4)) returns 2"
msgstr "AREAS((A1; A2:A4)) returnerar 2"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5274
#, no-c-format
msgid "CELL"
msgstr "CELL"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Returns information about position, formatting or contents in a reference."
msgstr ""
"Returnerar information om position, formatering eller innehåll i en referens."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5280
#, no-c-format
msgid "CELL(type; reference)"
msgstr "CELL(typ; referens)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5288
#, no-c-format
msgid "CELL(\"COL\", C7) returns 3"
msgstr "CELL(\"COL\",C7) returnerar 3"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5291
#, no-c-format
msgid "CELL(\"ROW\", C7) returns 7"
msgstr "CELL(\"ROW\", C7) returnerar 7"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5294
#, no-c-format
msgid "CELL(\"ADDRESS\", C7) returns $C$7"
msgstr "CELL(\"ADDRESS\", C7) returnerar $C$7"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5300
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHOOSE"
msgstr "CHOOSE"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Returns the parameter specified by the index."
msgstr "Returnerar parametern som anges av index."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5306
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHOOSE(index; parameter1; parameter2;...)"
msgstr "CHOOSE(index; parameter1; parameter2; ...)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5310
#, no-c-format
msgid "Index"
msgstr "Index"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:5311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "Argument"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5314
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHOOSE(1; \"1st\"; \"2nd\") returns \"1st\""
msgstr "CHOOSE(1; \"1:a\"; \"2:a\") returnerar \"1:a\""

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5317
#, no-c-format
msgid "CHOOSE(2; 3; 2; 4) returns 2"
msgstr "CHOOSE(2; 3; 2; 4) returnerar 2"

#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:5323
#, no-c-format
msgid "COLUMN"
msgstr "COLUMN"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The COLUMN function returns the column of given cell reference. If no "
"parameter is specified the column of the current cell gets returned."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen COLUMN returnerar kolumnen för en given cellreferens. Om ingen "
"parameter anges, returneras kolumnen för den aktuella cellen."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5329
#, no-c-format
msgid "COLUMN(reference)"
msgstr "COLUMN(referens)"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5336
#, no-c-format
msgid "COLUMN(A1) returns 1"
msgstr "COLUMN(A1) returnerar 1"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:5339
#, no-c-format
msgid "COLUMN(D2) returns 4"
msgstr "COLUMN(D2) returnerar 4"

#. Tag: member
#: functions.docbook:5343 functions.docbook:5575
#, no-c-format
