#. Tag: title
#: functions.docbook:9563
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND"
msgstr "FIND"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The FIND() function finds one text string (find_text) within another text "
"string (within_text) and returns the number of the starting point of "
"find_text, from the leftmost character of within_text."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen FIND() hittar en textsträng (söktext) i en annan textsträng "
"(text) och returnerar numret på startpositionen av söktext, från tecknet "
"längst till vänster i text."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9565
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Parameter start_num specifies the character at which to start the search. "
"The first character is character number 1. If start_num is omitted, it is "
"assumed to be 1."
msgstr ""
"Parametern startnummer anger tecknet där sökningen startar. Det första "
"tecknet har nummer 1. Om startnummer utelämnas, så antas det vara 1."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use function SEARCH, but unlike SEARCH, FIND is case-sensitive "
"and does not allow wildcard characters."
msgstr ""
"Du kan också använda funktionen SEARCH, men i motsats till SEARCH så är FIND "
"storlekskänslig och tillåter inte jokertecken."

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9571
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND(find_text;within_text;start_num)"
msgstr "FIND(söktext;text;startnummer)"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:9575 functions.docbook:9612 functions.docbook:10112
#: functions.docbook:10145
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text you want to find"
msgstr "Texten du vill söka efter"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:9576 functions.docbook:9613 functions.docbook:10113
#: functions.docbook:10146
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text which may contain find_text"
msgstr "Texten som kan innehålla söktext"

#. Tag: seg
#: functions.docbook:9577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specifies index to start the search"
msgstr "Anger ett index där sökningen ska starta"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9580
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND(\"Cal\";\"Calligra\") returns 1"
msgstr "FIND(\"Cal\";\"Calligra\") returnerar 1"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9583
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND(\"i\";\"Calligra\") returns 5"
msgstr "FIND(\"i\";\"Calligra\") returnerar 4"

#. Tag: para
#: functions.docbook:9586
#, no-c-format
msgid "FIND(\"a\";\"Sheets in Calligra\";4) returns 12"
msgstr "FIND(\"a\";\"Sheets i Calligra\";4) returnerar 12"

